{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_52_03",
  "title": "鈴村優 3話 創作意欲が大暴れです",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～……ほんまに今日はええ一日やなぁ\nコン・サドさんの新刊も無事手に入ったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa~… today’s really been a great day.\nI managed to get Con Sado-san’s new release safely‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "他にも、新しい同人誌との出会いが沢山あったわ～\nうちの創作活動にも、ええ刺激になりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and I discovered so many new doujinshi too~\nIt’s been such great inspiration for my own creative work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.3333332062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "特にコン・サドさんの新刊は……\nうちの心にふかーく刺さりましたわぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Especially Con Sado-san’s new book…\nit pierced straight through my heart~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.0982141614,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.7333332062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "残酷な世界の中、生まれた\n北海道の雪のように、儚い出会い……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A fleeting encounter‚ born within a cruel world‚\nlike Hokkaido’s snow…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "そしてあまたの試練を乗り越えていく中\n二人に芽生える強固な友情……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And as they overcome countless trials‚\nan unshakable friendship blossoms between the two…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.3000013988
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "うちが求めてたんは、こういうのやったんです！\n……どうしたんです？　そんな疲れた顔して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is exactly the kind of thing I’ve been craving!\n…What’s wrong? Why do you look so exhausted?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.2000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.1333347321
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あぁ……優の勢いに圧倒されてな……\nところで、目当ての本は一通り手に入れたんだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-oh… I’m just overwhelmed by your energy…\nAnyway‚ you got all the books you wanted‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.6630852383
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "はい、おかげさまで。もうたまりません……\nうちの創作意欲が大暴れです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ thanks to you. I can barely contain myself…\nMy creative urges are going completely wild!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.0964186987,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.4630852383
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あ…はは……同人誌もいいけど、そろそろご飯の時間だ\n実は近くに海鮮丼の名店があるんだ。そこに寄って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… haha… Doujinshi are great‚ but it’s about time to eat.\nThere’s actually a famous seafood bowl place nearby. I thought we could stop by—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "何言ってるんです、{user}さん\nうちらにそんな所に寄ってる時間なんてありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you talking about‚ {user}?\nWe have no time to stop somewhere like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.6353291195,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.2686587653
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "でも北海道に来たんだし、少しくらいうまい食事を……\n……待ってくれ。「時間がない」って、なんの話だ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But we came all the way to Hokkaido—at least let’s have some good food—\n…Wait. What do you mean‚ “no time”?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.0437381747
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "決まってます。これから旅館に戻って新刊の準備です\n言いましたよね？　うちの創作意欲が大暴れやって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Obviously—we’re going back to the inn to start working on my next book.\nI told you‚ didn’t I? My creative urges are going completely wild.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.8770716352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.877071508
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "ズバリ、次の新刊のテーマは……『北海道の雪』！\n儚く……そして繊細な友情を描きたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And the theme of my next release is… “Hokkaido Snow”!\nI want to depict a fragile… delicate friendship.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.3437383018,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.1437381747
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "今この北海道にいる間やないと描けません\nうちのインスピレーションが湧き上がってるうちに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can only draw it while I’m here in Hokkaido.\nWhile my inspiration is overflowing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.8104049685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.1770735426
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "今から同人誌を作るのか？　しかも旅行中に……？\n……まぁ、時間の使い方は自由だしな。頑張ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re starting a doujinshi right now? During the trip…?\n…Well‚ it’s your time to use. Do your best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "え？　{user}さん、なんでそんなに\n他人事みたいなこと言うんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? {user}‚ why are you talking\nlike it has nothing to do with you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.7535135908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.686846797
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "一緒に即売会に行って{user}さんと\n心が繋がり合ったと思ったのに……うち、悲しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After we went to the convention together‚\nI thought our hearts had connected… This makes me sad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.2201802574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり……うちにも、うちの趣味にも\n心の中では引いてはるんちゃいます……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe… deep down‚\nyou’re actually put off by me—and my hobbies…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.6868367515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.1201608024
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そんな訳ないだろ。優の趣味に恥じるところなんてない\n優のことも、優の趣味も、俺は心から応援してるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course not. There’s nothing shameful about your hobbies.\nI support you—and your passions—from the bottom of my heart.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.4073709491
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "嬉しい……{user}さんがうちのこと\nそんな風に思ってくれてるなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m so happy… to hear\n{user}-san thinks of me that way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.0740560535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "もし{user}さんが隣にいてくれたら\nうち、最後まで新刊を描き切れる気がします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you stay by my side‚\nI feel like I can finish this new book no matter what.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.3740631743,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
      "startTime": 177.1407114032
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、優の創作活動のサポートなら任せてくれ\n応援でもなんでも、出来ることならやらせてもらうよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ if it’s supporting your creative work‚ leave it to me.\nEncouragement or anything else—I’ll do whatever I can.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_doujinevent-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "doujinevent-00-noon",
      "startTime": 185.0000083609
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_52_03-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "本当に、なんでも……？　……よーし、そんなら\n早速旅館に戻りましょ！　沢山手伝ってもらいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really‚ anything…? …Alright then—\nLet’s head back to the inn right away! I’m going to have you help a lot!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.4333601319,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5766.642920000009,
          "startTime": 197.2000030519
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8189.9762532999885,
          "startTime": 199.6233363852
        }
